00:13:12,470 --> 00:13:14,869
Nisu cak ni hodali.

209
00:13:36,667 --> 00:13:38,668
Što?

210
00:13:39,167 --> 00:13:40,966
Ne razumijem što se dogaða.

211
00:13:40,967 --> 00:13:44,467
