212
00:13:44,566 --> 00:13:46,867
Htjeli su Boba imenovati šefom.

213
00:13:46,967 --> 00:13:48,865
I, naravno, ja se moram oženiti tobom.

214
00:13:48,866 --> 00:13:50,565
U cemu je problem?

215
00:13:50,566 --> 00:13:52,466
