kažnjiv s 250.000 $...-

264
00:16:55,153 --> 00:16:59,753
.. i kaznom zatvora u trajanju
od 5 god. u državnom zatvoru.

265
00:17:02,653 --> 00:17:06,052
Dakle, Andrew,

266
00:17:06,152 --> 00:17:09,852
želite mi nešto reci?

267
00:17:13,852 --> 00:17:15,851
Ne?

268
00:17:17,751 --> 00:17:20,051
Da?

269
00:17:23,851 --> 00:17:27,951
Istina je...

270
00:17:28,051 --> 00:17:32,251
Mr. Gilbertson, istina je...

271
00:17:32,850 --> 00:17:37,550
.. da smo Margaret i ja...

272
00:17:37,650 --> 00:17:43,649
Mi smo samo dvoje ljudi koje
se nije smjelo zaljubiti. Ali jesmo.

273
00:17:46,949 --> 00:17:48,949
Nismo mogli reci nikome u uredu,

274
00:17:48,950 --> 00:17:51,749
zbog mog velikog promaknuca
koje predstoji.

275
00:17:51,749 --> 00:17:53,748
Promaknuce?

276
00:17:53,749 --> 00:17:57,648
Oboje smo smatrali da bi bilo..

277
00:17:57,748 --> 00:18:00,748
neprilicno, ako bih bio
unaprijeðen za urednika,

278
00:18:00,748 --> 00:18:03,748
Urednik?
- Dok smo mi...

279
00:18:05,448 --> 00:18:11,347
Jeste li rekli roditeljima o
vašoj tajnoj ljubavi?

280
00:18:11,547 --> 00:18:14,847
Nemoguce, moji su roditelji mrtvi.

281
00:18:14,948 --> 00:18:17,247
I braca i sestre takoðer, tako da...

282
00:18:18,048 --> 00:18:19,746
I vaši su mrtvi?

283
