310
00:19:43,841 --> 00:19:45,440
I, molim te, potvrdi vegetarijanski obrok,

311
00:19:45,441 --> 00:19:52,040
jer su mi zadnji put pod vegetarijansku,
podvalili neku toplu, masnu salatu...

312
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:54,041
Zašto ne zapisuješ?

313
