Oprosti, zar ti nisi bila u istoj sobi?

314
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:59,039
Što je? Što?

315
00:19:59,040 --> 00:20:01,640
A, ono o tvom promaknucu?

316
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:04,640
