369
00:23:14,525 --> 00:23:17,325
Juneau? Mislila sam da idemo u Sitku.

370
00:23:17,325 --> 00:23:21,226
Idemo.
- I kako cemo doci do Sitke?

371
00:23:50,923 --> 00:23:54,423
Dobro. Pocinjemo.

372
