Ne bismo li trebali biti u hotelu?

398
00:26:11,313 --> 00:26:14,613
Otkazali smo vam rezervacije.
Obitelj ne odsjeda u hotelu.

399
00:26:14,613 --> 00:26:18,312
Bit cete kod nas doma.
- Super.

400
00:26:18,413 --> 00:26:20,012
Što?
- Bože.

401
00:26:20,013 --> 00:26:22,712
Pomozi se nogom za
podizanje ovoga.

402
00:26:22,712 --> 00:26:24,812
Andrew, pomozi joj s tim.

403
00:26:24,912 --> 00:26:27,712
Rado, ali mi ona ne da.

404
00:26:27,712 --> 00:26:30,912
Samostalna je. Feministkinja.

405
00:26:39,911 --> 00:26:42,410
Doði, dušo.

406
00:26:42,411 --> 00:26:45,610
Jesi li vidjela koje cipele ima?

407
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:58,409
Ovaj je posljednji.

408
00:26:59,210 --> 00:27:02,409
Pravilo 5 sekundi.
- Imam ga!

409
00:27:02,409 --> 00:27:05,508
Osušit ce se.

410
00:27:05,509 --> 00:27:07,308
Ne ulazim u taj camac.

411
00:27:07,309 --> 00:27:09,409
I ne moraš.
Vidimo se za par dana.

412
00:27:09,409 --> 00:27:11,308
Znaš da ne znam plivati.

413
00:27:11,309 --> 00:27:13,708
To je camac.

414
00:27:20,508 --> 00:27:22,208
Doði.

415
00:27:26,307 --> 00:27:28,208
Idemo.

416
00:27:35,207 --> 00:27:39,307
Dobro izgledaš, šefice.
Samo polako.

417
00:27:45,107 --> 00:27:47,406
Putuje s puno prtljage.

418
00:27:47,506 --> 00:27:49,706
Pridržat cu te.

419
00:27:50,706 --> 00:27:53,905
Makni ruku s guzice.
Makni.

420
00:27:56,306 --> 00:27:59,006
Eto te. Sišla si.

421
00:28:03,805 --> 00:28:07,105
cestitam, ostario sam cekajuci te.

422
00:28:33,903 --> 00:28:36,103
Evo nas kod kuce.

423
00:28:38,402 --> 00:28:40,503
Ovo je tvoja kuca!?

424
00:28:41,702 --> 00:28:44,202
Tko si ti?

425
00:28:58,201 --> 00:29:00,300
Zašto si mi rekao da si siromašan?

426
00:29:00,301 --> 00:29:02,801
Nisam to rekao.
- Ali nisi rekao da si bogat.

427
00:29:02,801 --> 00:29:04,699
Nisam ja bogat, nego moji roditelji.

428
00:29:04,700 --> 00:29:07,400
To svi bogataši kažu.

429
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,999
Hej, Andrew, dobro došao kuci!

430
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:11,800
Bok! Mama, što je ovo?

431
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:15,500
Ništa, mala zabava dobrodošlice.
Je li to zlocin?

432
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:18,699
Samo 50-ak najbližih
prijatelja i susjeda.

433
00:29:18,799 --> 00:29:21,999
Svi te jedva cekaju. Doðite.

434
00:29:22,099 --> 00:29:24,199
Zabava?
- Izgleda.

435
00:29:24,199 --> 00:29:27,699
Idemo, i moja se baka krece
brže od tebe.

436
00:29:28,599 --> 00:29:31,398
Što si to unutra natovarila?

437
00:29:35,498 --> 00:29:37,998
Drago mi je, Margaret.
Dobro došla u Sitku.

438
00:29:37,998 --> 00:29:40,198
Drago mi je.

439
00:29:40,298 --> 00:29:43,398
Zašto mi nisi rekao da ste vi
varijanta Kennedyjevih na Aljasci?

440
00:29:43,497 --> 00:29:47,098
Kako sam i mogao? Zadnje tri
godine smo pricali samo o tebi.

441
00:29:47,997 --> 00:29:51,097
Uspori malo. Ne možemo
ovako nastaviti.

442
00:29:51,097 --> 00:29:53,097
Ljudi trebaju pomisliti da smo
zaljubljeni, pa...

443
00:29:53,098 --> 00:29:57,297
Nema problema. Mogu se ja pretvarati
da sam zaljubljeni mladoženja.

444
00:29:57,396 --> 00:30:01,596
Ali ti se moraš uživiti u price
o djeci i sve to..

445
00:30:01,696 --> 00:30:04,396
Jako smiješno. Kad cemo tvojima
reci da smo zaruceni?

446
00:30:04,396 --> 00:30:08,596
Izabrat cu pravi trenutak.
- Hej, Andrew. Bok!

447
00:30:08,696 --> 00:30:12,795
Gðo. McKittrick, kako ste?
Drago mi je da vas vidim.

448
00:30:12,895 --> 00:30:14,694
Gdine McKittrick. Ovo je Margaret.

449
00:30:14,695 --> 00:30:16,194
Drago mi je.

450
00:30:16,195 --> 00:30:17,895
Dobar dan kako ste?
Drago mi je.

451
00:30:17,896 --> 00:30:21,295
Znaš, oduvijek sam se pitala:
što radi književni urednik?

452
00:30:21,295 --> 00:30:23,395
To je pravo pitanje, Louise.

453
00:30:23,495 --> 00:30:25,595
I mene zanima odgovor.

454
00:30:26,894 --> 00:30:29,394
Bok, tata.
- Sine.

455
00:30:29,394 --> 00:30:32,394
Ti mora da si Maggy.
- Margaret.

456
00:30:33,194 --> 00:30:36,293
Joe, drago mi je što sam te upoznao.
- I meni je drago.

457
00:30:36,394 --> 00:30:40,294
Zašto nam ne kažeš što tocno
radi književni urednik?

458
00:30:40,394 --> 00:30:43,993
Osim što izvodi pisce na
rucak i opija se.

459
00:30:44,094 --> 00:30:47,793
To zvuci zabavno. Nije cudo
što voliš biti urednik.

460
00:30:47,793 --> 00:30:51,493
Ne, Andrew nije urednik.
On je pomocnik urednika.

461
00:30:51,592 --> 00:30:54,592
Maggy je urednik.
- Margaret.

462
00:30:54,692 --> 00:30:58,393
Vi ste, zapravo, Andrewova šefica?

463
00:30:58,492 --> 00:31:00,792
Ma vidi ti to.

464
00:31:01,592 --> 00:31:05,292
Idem po još jedno.

465
00:31:05,692 --> 00:31:07,392
Šarmantno.

466
00:31:11,892 --> 00:31:16,091
Odlican prvi utisak, tata.
- Kojeg vraga, Andrew?

467
00:31:16,191 --> 00:31:18,991
Pojaviš se nakon toliko vremena,
s tom ženom koju mrziš,

468
00:31:19,091 --> 00:31:20,889
i sad ti je djevojka?
- Tek smo stigli.

469
00:31:20,890 --> 00:31:23,590
Možemo li pricekati par sekundi
prije nego se pocupamo?

470
00:31:23,690 --> 00:31:26,290
Nisam nikad mislio da si tip
koji spava s onakvima.

471
00:31:26,290 --> 00:31:28,389
Ta žena je, zapravo,

472
00:31:28,390 --> 00:31:29,989
jedan od najcjenjenijih
urednika u gradu.

473
00:31:29,990 --> 00:31:32,990
Ona ti služi kao ulaznica, da
možeš posjetiti majku.

474
00:31:33,090 --> 00:31:36,990
Nije ona moja ulaznica,
ona mi je zarucnica.

475
00:31:37,090 --> 00:31:38,489
Što si rekao?

476
00:31:38,490 --> 00:31:40,989
cuo si me. Ženim se.

477
00:31:44,689 --> 00:31:46,889
Kako ste?
- Dobro.

478
00:31:46,889 --> 00:31:49,689
Želite malo...?
- Ne, hvala.

479
00:31:49,789 --> 00:31:52,489
To je tradicija.
- Radi se o sastojcima.

480
00:31:52,489 --> 00:31:54,487
Baš ne obožavam ribe.
- Svidjet ce vam se.

481
00:31:54,488 --> 00:31:58,788
Lijepo, ali...
- Probajte.

482
00:32:03,388 --> 00:32:06,588
Dame i gospodo, imam važnu objavu!

483
00:32:06,687 --> 00:32:09,188
Margaret i ja cemo se vjencati.

484
00:32:10,187 --> 00:32:12,587
Oprostite.
- U redu je.

485
00:32:12,687 --> 00:32:16,187
Može se oprati.

486
00:32:17,287 --> 00:32:19,586
Dušo, gdje si?

487
00:32:19,686 --> 00:32:21,587
Evo je.

488
00:32:23,886 --> 00:32:26,086
Doði, draga.

489
00:32:31,286 --> 00:32:34,386
Evo je, dame i gospodo, tu je.

490
00:32:34,485 --> 00:32:39,485
cestitamo, Andrew.
- Hvala.

491
00:32:40,185 --> 00:32:43,485
Dajte šampanjac.

492
00:32:44,785 --> 00:32:48,085
Znaci, to je po tebi bio savršen
trenutak za objavu zaruka?

493
00:32:48,185 --> 00:32:49,585
Odlicno.

494
00:32:49,684 --> 00:32:51,283
Andrew, bok.

495
00:32:51,284 --> 00:32:54,284
O, Bože moj, Gert, bok!

496
00:32:55,384 --> 00:32:57,884
Kako si?
Nisam znao da si tu.

497
00:32:57,884 --> 00:33:02,483
Tvoja mama je htjela da to bude
iznenaðenje. Pa, iznenaðenje!

498
00:33:02,683 --> 00:33:05,883
I potpuno smo bezobrazni. Bok.

499
00:33:05,883 --> 00:33:09,283
O.
- Ovo je moja bivš...

500
00:33:09,383 --> 00:33:12,383
Gertrude. Možeš me zvati Gert.

501
00:33:12,483 --> 00:33:15,483
cestitam oboma.
- Hvala.

502
00:33:15,583 --> 00:33:18,282
Jesam li propustila pricu?

503
00:33:18,282 --> 00:33:20,281
Kakvu pricu?
- Kakvu pricu?

504
00:33:20,282 --> 00:33:22,081
O tome kako si je zaprosio.

505
00:33:22,082 --> 00:33:26,482
Nacin prosidbe puno govori o
muškarcevu karakteru.

506
00:33:26,582 --> 00:33:28,181
Da..
- Zaista.

507
00:33:28,182 --> 00:33:32,081
Voljeli bismo cuti,
Andrew, hoceš nam ispricati?

508
00:33:35,481 --> 00:33:37,081
Znate što?

509
00:33:37,181 --> 00:33:40,080
Margaret voli to pricati.

510
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:42,680
Prepustit cu to njoj.

511
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:45,380
Mi cemo sjesti i slušati.

512
00:33:47,981 --> 00:33:51,880
Gdje zapoceti?
Prica...

513
00:33:51,980 --> 00:33:53,879
Pa..

514
00:33:59,979 --> 00:34:02,679
Andrew i ja...

515
00:34:02,679 --> 00:34:06,579
Uskoro cemo proslaviti našu
prvu godišnjicu.

516
00:34:06,679 --> 00:34:09,979
Znala sam da je nestrpljiv
da me zaprosi,

517
00:34:10,079 --> 00:34:13,178
a bio je preplašen kao pticica.

518
00:34:13,278 --> 00:34:16,078
Pa sam ga povremeno ohrabrivala,

519
00:34:16,178 --> 00:34:18,778
jer sam znala da nema
hrabrosti pitati...

520
00:34:18,778 --> 00:34:21,577
Pa nije baš tako bilo.

521
00:34:21,677 --> 00:34:23,878
Ne?
- Ne, ne.

522
00:34:23,878 --> 00:34:25,977
Davao sam naznake,

523
00:34:26,177 --> 00:34:28,677
ali ova je žena suptilna
k'o pištolj.

524
00:34:28,677 --> 00:34:33,377
Bojao sam se da ce naci kutijicu...

525
00:34:33,577 --> 00:34:36,677
Kutijicu koju je ukrasio kolažom.

526
00:34:36,677 --> 00:34:41,476
Izrezao je svoje slike u
sitne djelice...

527
00:34:41,576 --> 00:34:45,276
.. i njima prekrio kutiju.
Prekrasno.

528
00:34:45,376 --> 00:34:49,575
Otvorila sam tu ukrašenu
kutiju i vidjela..

529
00:34:49,676 --> 00:34:53,975
.. mala srca napravljena od konfeta.

530
00:34:54,075 --> 00:34:58,675
Ispod njih sam vidjela najljepši...

531
00:34:58,775 --> 00:35:01,175
Ništa...
Nije biloprestena.

532
00:35:01,275 --> 00:35:03,373
Nije bilo prstena?
- Što?

533
00:35:03,374 --> 00:35:07,874
Ne. U kutiji, ispod svog tog smeca,

534
00:35:07,974 --> 00:35:11,774
bio je papir s adresom hotela,

535
00:35:11,874 --> 00:35:16,574
datum i vrijeme,
u stilu Humfrey Bogarta.

536
00:35:16,674 --> 00:35:18,873
Muški.

537
00:35:18,973 --> 00:35:20,673
U svakom slucaju,
Margaret...

538
00:35:20,674 --> 00:35:24,573
Mislila sam da se viða s drugom.
Bilo je to strašno.

539
00:35:24,673 --> 00:35:28,973
Ipak sam otišla u hotel.
Zalupala sam na vrata,

540
00:35:29,073 --> 00:35:33,173
ali su bila otkljucana.
I kad sam ih širom otvorila,

541
00:35:33,273 --> 00:35:34,772
bio je tamo...

542
00:35:34,773 --> 00:35:36,172
Stajao.
- Klecao.

543
00:35:36,173 --> 00:35:37,971
Poput muškarca.
- Na krevetu posutom laticama ruža,

544
00:35:37,972 --> 00:35:41,772
u smokingu.
Vaš sin...

545
00:35:41,872 --> 00:35:45,672
Grcao je od suza.

546
00:35:45,772 --> 00:35:48,672
Kad je uhvatio dah,

547
00:35:48,772 --> 00:35:50,370
rekao mi je...
- Hoceš li se udati za mene?

548
00:35:50,371 --> 00:35:52,170
Ona je rekla, da. I gotovo.

549
00:35:52,171 --> 00:35:55,471
Gladan sam.

550
00:35:56,171 --> 00:35:58,970
Kakva prica.

551
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:03,170
Prekrasna.
- Andy, tako si osjecajan.

552
00:36:03,971 --> 00:36:06,670
Rukotvorina od konfeta.

553
00:36:06,770 --> 00:36:09,470
Hej, da vidimo poljubac.

554
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:12,470
Poljubac.
- Ne.

555
00:36:14,469 --> 00:36:18,169
Dobro, dobro.
Evo ga. Spremni?

556
00:36:19,669 --> 00:36:23,169
Što je ovo? Mora biti na usta, za ozbiljno.

557
00:36:23,269 --> 00:36:27,369
Poljubi je!

558
00:36:27,469 --> 00:36:31,068
Poljubi je!

559
00:36:31,168 --> 00:36:32,768
Dobro!

560
00:36:34,068 --> 00:36:36,368
Dobro, idemo.

561
00:36:40,767 --> 00:36:43,767
Andy, pravi poljubac!

562
00:36:45,067 --> 00:36:48,167
Pravi.
- Možeš ti to.

563
00:37:09,965 --> 00:37:13,265
Tako sam sretna zbog vas!

564
00:37:13,466 --> 00:37:15,565
Tako sretna!

565
00:37:15,665 --> 00:37:17,865
Otvorimo šampanjac!

566
00:37:18,765 --> 00:37:20,665
I evo nas.

567
00:37:22,164 --> 00:37:25,765
Ovo je vaša spavaca soba.

568
00:37:27,164 --> 00:37:31,164
Prekrasna je, a tek pogled.

569
00:37:31,464 --> 00:37:33,664
A ovo je krevet.

570
00:37:33,664 --> 00:37:35,764
Izvrstan krevet!

571
00:37:35,864 --> 00:37:38,564
A gdje je Andrewova soba?

572
00:37:38,564 --> 00:37:43,663
Dušo, ne zavaramo se da vas
dvoje ne spavate u istom krevetu.

573
00:37:43,763 --> 00:37:45,863
Spavat ce ovdje s tobom.

574
00:37:45,963 --> 00:37:49,063
Super, jer se volimo
stiskati, zar ne, dušo?

575
00:37:49,163 --> 00:37:51,162
Mi smo stiskavci.

576
00:37:51,163 --> 00:37:53,463
O, Bože moj, što je to?

577
00:37:53,563 --> 00:37:56,563
Kevin...
- Slatkic mali.

578
00:37:56,563 --> 00:37:59,462
Tko je to?
- To je Kevin.

579
00:37:59,562 --> 00:38:01,962
Oprosti, Margaret.
- Baš je sladak.

580
00:38:02,062 --> 00:38:04,462
Spasili smo ga iz šinteraja,

581
00:38:04,462 --> 00:38:06,061
i još ga treniramo, oprosti.

582
00:38:06,062 --> 00:38:09,961
Pazi da ti ne pobjegne van.
Zgrabit ce ga orlovi.

583
00:38:09,961 --> 00:38:13,861
Ma ne slušaj je, samo
se šali, zar ne?

584
00:38:13,961 --> 00:38:17,960
Tu su vam ciste plahte,
jastucnice, rucnici...

585
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:23,161
Ako vam bude prohladno, uzmite ovo.
Ima posebne moci.

586
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:25,760
Kakve posebne moci?

587
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:28,060
Ja ga zovem
"stvarateljem beba."

588
00:38:28,160 --> 00:38:32,560
Onda moramo biti jako
oprezni s tim.

589
00:38:32,660 --> 00:38:34,558
Nemoj ga tamo staviti.
- Idemo.

590
00:38:34,559 --> 00:38:37,359
Bila je duga vecer.
Laku noc svima.

591
00:38:37,459 --> 00:38:39,358
Laku noc.
- Laku noc.

592
00:38:39,359 --> 00:38:40,759
Laku noc.

593
00:38:40,859 --> 00:38:43,058
Hvala.
- Hvala.

594
00:38:43,059 --> 00:38:45,558
Laku noc.
- Laku noc.

595
00:38:47,659 --> 00:38:51,158
Laku noc.
- Bila je lijepa vecer, hvala.

596
00:38:51,258 --> 00:38:54,858
Slatko sanjajte. Bok
- Bok.

597
00:38:56,358 --> 00:38:59,158
Nisi dugo bio doma.

598
00:38:59,258 --> 00:39:02,557
Nisam imao puno odmora
u zadnje tri godine.

599
00:39:02,657 --> 00:39:04,758
Prestani se žaliti.

600
00:39:09,157 --> 00:39:11,056
Nemoj gledati, u redu?

601
00:39:11,057 --> 00:39:12,657
U redu.

602
00:39:13,857 --> 00:39:16,456
Jesu ti oci zatvorene?
- Potpuno.

603
00:39:16,556 --> 00:39:19,856
Sigurno?
- Da, sigurno.

604
00:39:28,256 --> 00:39:31,855
Ovu si pidžamu uzela na Aljasku.

605
00:39:31,855 --> 00:39:35,555
Da, jer sam trebala biti
u hotelu, sama.

606
00:39:35,655 --> 00:39:38,755
Sjecaš se?
- Možemo li jednostavno spavati?

607
00:39:39,754 --> 00:39:41,955
Odlicno.

608
00:40:10,153 --> 00:40:12,452
Pa..

609
00:40:12,553 --> 00:40:16,252
.. baš se i necu naspavati
dok mi sunce blješti u oci.

610
00:40:23,051 --> 00:40:24,551
Hvala.

611
00:40:45,850 --> 00:40:47,948
Andrew, mobitel.

612
00:40:47,949 --> 00:40:49,550
Andrew.

613
00:40:53,449 --> 00:40:57,049
Andrew?
- Aha.

614
00:41:00,449 --> 00:41:04,149
Andrew, gdje je?
- Torba, bocni džep.

615
00:41:08,748 --> 00:41:12,548
Halo, halo.

616
00:41:12,648 --> 00:41:17,247
Frank, dragi, jesi tamo?
Halo?

617
00:41:17,348 --> 00:41:21,647
Imam ocajan prijem!
Daj mi minutu!

618
00:41:21,947 --> 00:41:23,747
Moj Bože! Margaret!

619
00:41:23,748 --> 00:41:27,147
Molim? Samo trenutak.

620
00:41:27,247 --> 00:41:28,847
Ne, ne.

621
00:41:29,847 --> 00:41:33,646
Frank, žao mi je što si
pod pritiskom.

622
00:41:34,046 --> 00:41:37,846
Naravno da želim da
budeš sretan.

623
00:41:38,146 --> 00:41:40,846
Frank? Frank?
Frank zlato.

624
00:41:40,846 --> 00:41:43,346
Bit ce sve u redu.

625
00:41:43,445 --> 00:41:46,046
Mogu ga nazvati i otkazati.

626
00:41:50,246 --> 00:41:52,545
Potpuno si u pravu, Frank.

627
00:41:52,845 --> 00:41:55,045
Da, Frank, naravno da te slušam.

628
00:41:55,045 --> 00:41:58,944
Da, volim te slušati, Frank.

629
00:41:59,845 --> 00:42:02,345
Sjedni!

630
00:42:02,844 --> 00:42:05,144
Ne, ne ti, Frank.

631
00:42:05,245 --> 00:42:07,644
Frank, ako mogu prijeci na stvar,

632
00:42:07,644 --> 00:42:10,544
mislim da bi bila greška da se povuceš.

633
00:42:10,744 --> 00:42:13,744
Zato, Frank, jer si tolike godine...

634
00:42:13,844 --> 00:42:16,544
Inspirirao si me svojim prekrasnim rijecima,

635
00:42:16,544 --> 00:42:19,244
i osjecam...
Tiho, pricam na mobitel.

636
00:42:19,344 --> 00:42:22,543
Vrijeme je da i svijet uživa
u tvojim rijecima.

637
00:42:22,643 --> 00:42:25,343
Prepune su strasti...

638
00:42:25,343 --> 00:42:29,143
i mislim da trebaju biti date...

639
00:42:29,342 --> 00:42:31,943
Frank, samo...

640
00:42:32,042 --> 00:42:34,743
samo želim da budeš sretan.
Daj mi tog psa!

641
00:42:35,042 --> 00:42:37,342
Trebam... Frank, možeš
li malo pricekati?

642
00:42:37,342 --> 00:42:39,942
