709
00:45:53,328 --> 00:45:56,526
Natjeralo me na razmišljanje.

710
00:45:56,527 --> 00:45:58,326
Puno sam postigao u životu,

711
00:45:58,327 --> 00:46:01,828
Prakticki sam izgradio carstvo s
