741
00:47:28,421 --> 00:47:31,821
Evo tog velikog iznenaðenja.

742
00:47:31,921 --> 00:47:33,521
Spremna?

743
00:47:35,320 --> 00:47:38,620
Margaret, svidjet ce ti se!

744
00:48:07,418 --> 00:48:10,418
Ramon je jedini egzoticni
plesac na otoku.

745
00:48:10,518 --> 00:48:13,118
Sretni smo što ga imamo.

746
00:48:21,617 --> 00:48:25,217
Ramon, ovdje.

747
00:48:25,617 --> 00:48:27,417
Ovdje.

748
00:48:27,517 --> 00:48:29,017
Ovamo.

749
